t remembrance, best supplication","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 4, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Abdullah reported: The\u00a0Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe best\u00a0remembrance is to declare there is no God but Allah. The best\u00a0supplication is to declare all praise is due to Allah.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3383 Grade:\u00a0Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062c\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u0631\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11634,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/22\/dua-oppressed-kafir\/","url_meta":{"origin":24647,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Fear supplications of oppressed, even unbelievers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 22, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBeware of the supplication of the oppressed, even if he is an unbeliever, for there is nothing to block it.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 12549 Grade:\u00a0Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}]